articles.title: 2024 Paris Olympics: Shooter Rhythm Sangwan Secures Record 16th Olympic Quota - The Quint
articles.description: Rhythm Sangwan nailed a record 16th Paris 2024 Olympics quota place for Indian in Shooting, winning bronze in the women’s 25m pistol, at the on-going Asia Olympic Qualification Rifle/Pistol here on Thursday.
articles.content: South Korea had already secured two quotas in the womens 25m pistol from previous qualifying events. That meant that Rhythm would have to finish better than at least three of the four remaining final… [+444 chars]
